HEADWORD: Unvisard
<hw>Un*vis"ard</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos> <ety>[1st pref.
<ets>un-</ets> + <ets>vizard</ets>.]</ety> <def>To take the vizard or
mask from; to unmask.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>unvizard</asp>.]</altsp> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Milton.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
